{"tid":1036132,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港做廣告creative喺咪要預咗比人抄?","createTime":"2019-02-25T04:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T06:14:38.000Z","uid":114175,"like":11,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d73273d668af5f8cb7e7a04557b127c65045f542","tid":1036132,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:27:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟最近開始搵啲freelance做，咁就喺會幫啲中小型facebook page做吓content呀graphic呀之類。好好彩搵到間公司明知我冇經驗都比我試，仲要其實間公司一向喺行開保守路線，都肯接受我啲新派啲嘅諗法，真喺好多謝佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但喺今日突然間發現有個行家，張圖同個campaign嘅idea喺可以話一模一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ACjcAS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ACjcAS.png&h=42996229&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8iKoHx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8iKoHx.png&h=2d534e18&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n雖然唔喺話花咗好多時間心機喺依個campaign上面，但我一睇到比人咁抄個吓真係灰鳩咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我明白依啲情況可能時時都有發生，但喺咪就喺依種咁差嘅抄襲風氣，搞到香港好少創作嘅人材呢? 其實依我所知，抄我post間公司都算喺一間start-up，我一向以為start-up會尊重創意多啲，原來喺我自己諗多咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港做creative嘅命運就係比人抄，做好自己就算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁介意比人抄就轉行啦"},{"pid":"74ec301012c0e7eaa87b8b37b5f7970cb3832632","tid":1036132,"uid":39496,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"下 你本身果果都唔覺得有咩creative既成分喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba8609c7f3ed5e024b943998e3212ee4c741d71","tid":1036132,"uid":59989,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"樓主呢張使唔使半個鐘做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6025b73f6ba3c84abe9f75fb7